{"tid":2132710,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"吉林省副公安廳長賀電出版《平安經》","createTime":"2020-07-30T14:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T16:45:22.000Z","uid":17232,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bc62f218741ff91d5a195ea96670e2874c8f6600","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"《平安經》為中國吉林省公安廳黨委副書記、常務副廳長賀電所著之書。該書標稱由人民出版社及群眾出版社聯合出版，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGT5L3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGT5L3n.jpg&h=b48962e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吉林省公安廳常務副廳長賀電出版一本名為《平安經》的書，當局正式介入調查。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經卷內容：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b617eWV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb617eWV.png&h=de65f88e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5i13Qg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5i13Qg.jpg&h=5dd404ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評論者張詠形容該書為<span class=\"x-large\">「中期傳世的經類大作力作，是歷代和當代僅見的首部平安經書」</span>，內容<span class=\"x-large\">「字字珠璣，句句精妙；滌蕩靈魂，惺惜共鳴；濃縮理念，參悟極深」「官員閱讀此書，領悟初心使命。學者閱讀此書，頓悟平安哲理。商賈閱讀此書，企業平安無虞。民眾閱讀此書，安享世間太平」。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4f6ea709d2a837ef839645ee5cb5baa3a920167b","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"2020年6月7日，中共吉林省委政法委員會，省委宣傳部，省文聯，團省委，長春日報社等單位還共同主辦了《平安經》的朗誦活動研討會。"},{"pid":"0f178246787d010927ee10056923560f5de243f9","tid":2132710,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b1a0612aa289dc5261c9a168c77bde569de447","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"中國痴撚左線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc023ee4f472659b68a2ebfec34c1bcdddd84e8","tid":2132710,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4b1a0612aa289dc5261c9a168c77bde569de447","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"中國痴撚左線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共產黨本身就係一個邪教組織"},{"pid":"9aca9135b4b6ffbd57d2302551f58b9035f845d1","tid":2132710,"uid":274435,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"屌賀電原來係人名"},{"pid":"cff93338506686ff3fba6fb912160bc1ccc51fdf","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>省應急管理廳、省人民政府新聞辦則多次宣傳、吹捧《平安經》<br />\n</strong><br />\n據中國傳媒報道，吉林省官方曾以多個途徑吹捧《平安經》。今年4月9日，吉林省應急管理廳通過官方微信公眾號分享書籍出版消息，評價該書「值得一讀」。<br />\n<br />\n5月9日，吉林省應急管理廳再度通過官方微信公眾號，發佈作者為張詠的一篇〈拜讀《平安經》感言〉，內文寫到：「從他的新作《平安經》中，令人感知到一位學者深邃的靈魂和寬廣的情懷。」<br />\n<br />\n據吉林省應急管理廳在官方微信公眾號的介紹，賀電是法學博士、書法文獻學博士、教授、博士研究生導師，同時是一級警監、享受國務院特殊津貼專家。<br />\n<br />\n吉林省人民政府新聞辦公室則在官方網站上，介紹《平安經》是「以經為載體，以歌訣、歌文形式撰寫的平安頌歌」。介紹提到，賀電曾在「公益朗誦活動研討會」上分享創作初衷及心得，與會學者、詩人暢談讀後感後，一同誦讀《平安經》。<br />\n<br />\n原文：《晚報：吉林省公安副廳長出版《平安經》引發輿論質疑，省委宣佈展開調查》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200729-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200729-evening-brief%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=701ef556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200729-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media 版權所有 翻印必究"},{"pid":"9e6fb8f6010d5a9ca1ba5f398288bfc14f3efd0e","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>《平安經》全書僅不斷重複「（...）平安」格式句子</strong><br />\n<br />\n根據網上轉載的書本內容，《平安經》分成多個篇章，但各篇只由不斷重複的「（...）平安」格式句子組成。在《人類眾生平安》一篇，「各性別平安」一節的內容為「男性平安，女性平安」，而「各年齡平安」一節的內容則為「初生平安，滿月平安，百天平安，1歲平安，2歲平安，3歲平安......」。<br />\n<br />\n在另一個題為《國家地區平安》的篇章，賀電寫道：「中華人民共和國平安，阿富汗平安，阿拉伯聯合酋長國平安，阿曼平安，阿塞拜疆平安（...）埃及平安，埃塞俄比亞平安，安哥拉平安......」<br />\n<br />\n在《中國各界平安》的篇章，有「中國公眾場所平安」部份，其下包括「中華機場平安」、「中華火車站平安」、「中華港口平安」等章節。<br />\n<br />\n原文：《晚報：吉林省公安副廳長出版《平安經》引發輿論質疑，省委宣佈展開調查》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200729-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200729-evening-brief%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=701ef556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200729-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media 版權所有 翻印必究"},{"pid":"b418ed6d3f1da02bd5a76dc3dd21297820211734","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9aca9135b4b6ffbd57d2302551f58b9035f845d1","tid":2132710,"uid":274435,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"屌賀電原來係人名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為係發來賀電"},{"pid":"3adf055705f0753de52de8f9cfd42771aa896259","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc023ee4f472659b68a2ebfec34c1bcdddd84e8","tid":2132710,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4b1a0612aa289dc5261c9a168c77bde569de447","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"中國痴撚左線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共產黨本身就係一個邪教組織"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我 發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711275d498b15dedd989989929667b2f50141d47","tid":2132710,"uid":331421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"啲經文咁撚戇鳩，乜撚野弱智經嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b05a6dc1edd31d9eb183728cfb964429a0d99e","tid":2132710,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"冇習近平平安<br />\n<br />\n冇就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871f92b49e6d0c80ee878c1c28f7150be361086e","tid":2132710,"uid":84339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:11:10.000Z","msg":"一隻綿羊，兩隻綿羊，三隻綿羊。。。"},{"pid":"ef7b169ff6555384e5dfa7aba88362ff64303c81","tid":2132710,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"711275d498b15dedd989989929667b2f50141d47","tid":2132710,"uid":331421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"啲經文咁撚戇鳩，乜撚野弱智經嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"係咪stone撚左"},{"pid":"625c412f0007278efe9fdedce2eccbc4d7eaa2ff","tid":2132710,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"我睇緊D乜撚野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d015716d9a5c1f2a26ebfac3709da7b4b1ed70ca","tid":2132710,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:14:0